description: Reference libraries for Project Arrhythmia modding
releaseNotes:
# 24.11.3 [alpha]
*bug fixes and improvements*

## Features
- Add pulse effect to P rank levels and add rank preview to arcade menus.
- Leaderboard scores use all score data for ranking.

## Changes
- New loading screen messages.
- Objects are now generated using a persistent hashing algorithm.

## Fixes
- Remove unneeded lastdateplayed from arcade save data.
- Handle volumes better for more consistent effects across the game's scenes.
- Fix for story levels not being able to save / load in pause menu.
- Fix for scores not being calculated on whole data.
- Fix for general UI getting borked after exiting editor.

## Known Issues
- There are still some issues with the new dragging editor feature.

## All leaderboards have been reset for this build. Unfortunately this is necessary to ensure that the new scoring system is working correctly. This should be the last time the leaderboards need a reset.

# [Alpha] -> [Default]
This build is a release candidate build for default. Assuming no major / game breaking bugs are found within 2 days, this build will be promoted to default.
